00:17:50,021 --> 00:17:51,053
這一切...
All this...

195
00:17:53,004 --> 00:17:54,045
來構建我們的新生活
to start our new life.

196
00:17:57,009 --> 00:17:59,027
現在我在想，為啥要這麼麻煩呢？
Now I wonder, why bother?

197
00:18:01,074 --> 00:18:05,080
因為你承諾在湖邊造一間木頭屋子
Because you promised to build a log cabin on a lake.

198
00:18:16,003 --> 00:18:17,067
這是他的最愛
This was his favorite.

199
00:18:18,002 --> 00:18:20,040
有品位的人
A man of taste.

200
00:18:20,045 --> 00:18:21,095
純正
Straight up.

201
00:18:21,095 --> 00:18:24,060
不加冰，不加水，不要後輔酒
No ice, no water, no chaser.

202
00:18:24,090 --> 00:18:26,087
什麼都不加
No shit.

203
00:18:31,048 --> 00:18:32,053
華特
Walter?

204
00:18:32,070 --> 00:18:33,077
入鄉隨俗吧
When in Rome

205
00:18:36,085 --> 00:18:38,096
敬所有離開的好人們
To all the good people gone to soon.

206
00:18:39,074 --> 00:18:41,050
願我們能銘記
May we remember that.

207
00:18:41,099 --> 00:18:43,089
記住這一切
Remember that.

208
00:19:23,089 --> 00:19:24,096
克尼斯
Chris.

209
00:19:28,001 --> 00:19:30,052
他們違背了一個直接命令
They disobeyed a direct order.

210
00:19:32,000 --> 00:19:33,058
她葬了她的丈夫
She buried her husband.

211
00:19:33,058 --> 00:19:35,086
不，卡倫！ 不是這樣的，他們不相信我
No, Karine, it's not that. They don't trust me.

212
00:19:35,086 --> 00:19:37,043
而且他們不信任我領導這個任務的原因
And they don't trust me for the same reason

213
00:19:37,043 --> 00:19:39,037
和公司不信任我的原因一樣
the company didn't trust me to lead this mission.

214
00:19:39,037 --> 00:19:41,061
因為你不是個堅守信念的人
Because you can't be a person of faith.

215
00:19:41,061 --> 00:19:44,076
也不能指望你做出符合理性的決定
And be counted on to make qualified rational decisions.

216
00:19:45,027 --> 00:19:48,064
你是個極端主義者，你知道，你是個瘋子
You're an extremist. You know, you're a lunatic.

217
00:19:48,084 --> 00:19:51,038
當我們到達我們要去的地方
When we get to where we're going

218
00:19:51,088 --> 00:19:55,061
這些人不會是你的船員了，他們會是你的鄰居
This people won't be your crew anymore. They will be your neighbors.

219
00:19:55,081 --> 00:19:57,011
請記住
Remember that.

220
00:19:58,036 --> 00:20:00,055
友善對待，好嗎？
Tread softly, okay?

221
00:20:08,064 --> 00:20:10,015
法拉斯，你能聽得見我嗎？
Faris, can you hear me?

222
00:20:10,035 --> 00:20:11,045
可以
Copy.

223
00:20:11,055 --> 00:20:12,083
開始吧
Let's do it.

224
00:20:15,064 --> 00:20:18,003
該死，你們都應該來看看這個風景
Damn, y'all should see this view.

225
00:20:18,013 --> 00:20:21,020
除非你把攝像環給修好，不然我們什麼也看不見
We can't see anything until you get the camera ring fixed.

226
00:20:21,039 --> 00:20:23,093
親愛的，為什麼你不朝該死的窗外看看呢
Why don't you look out the damn window, hon?

227
00:20:24,015 --> 00:20:26,029
安可，快啊，我們來恢覆電源吧
Ankor, come on, let's get this power back up,

228
00:20:26,039 --> 00:20:28,088
這樣大家就能欣賞這個美麗的風景了
so these people can enjoy the beautiful view.

229
00:20:29,048 --> 00:20:30,091
快好了
Almost there.

230
00:20:32,089 --> 00:20:34,091
好的，安可，你就位了就跟我說一聲
Alright, Ankor, let me know when you're in a position.

231
00:20:34,091 --> 00:20:36,065
我們就可以開始盡情搞事情了
We can get this party started.

232
00:20:36,085 --> 00:20:38,036
我已就位
I'm in position.

233
00:21:08,008 --> 00:21:09,029
已連接
Contact.

234
00:21:17,093 --> 00:21:19,058
小田，一切順利嗎？
All good, Tee?

235
00:21:20,004 --> 00:21:22,010
好的，我們這兒搞定了
Alright, we are clear.

236
00:21:22,012 --> 00:21:23,042
把帆拉起來
Reel her in.

237
00:21:23,045 --> 00:21:25,015
沒問題
Alright.

238
00:21:25,062 --> 00:21:28,044
小田，連接好絞盤
Winch engaging, Tee.

239
00:21:29,095 --> 00:21:31,068
正在把帆捲進來
Reeling her in.

240
00:21:34,089 --> 00:21:36,062
搞定，輕而易舉
Working like a dream.

241
00:21:51,022 --> 00:21:52,026
這就好
There we go.

242
00:21:52,051 --> 00:21:53,061
系統恢復了
And we are back up.

243
00:21:53,064 --> 00:21:54,094
小田，幹得漂亮
Well done Tee.

244
00:21:54,096 --> 00:21:56,014
我們下麵的系統重生了
We're alive down here,

245
00:21:56,034 --> 00:21:57,044
快點
come on.

246
00:21:57,064 --> 00:21:58,095
你們現在可別把我丟下就走了
Don't leave without me now.

247
00:21:59,005 --> 00:22:01,069
長官，我可以申請把他丟下嗎？
Permission to leave without him, sir?

248
00:22:01,079 --> 00:22:02,097
丹尼，歡迎回來
Welcome back, Danny.

249
00:22:03,094 --> 00:22:05,025
謝謝
Thanks.

250
00:22:05,045 --> 00:22:07,035
好的，我的活也幹完了，小田
Alright, that's me done, Tee.

251
00:22:07,055 --> 00:22:09,026
沒問題，我會跟著你回去的
Alright, I'm following you in.

252
00:22:09,046 --> 00:22:12,024
請為勞苦的我們備上冰啤
Please have a cold beer ready for the weary traveler.

253
00:22:12,031 --> 00:22:15,058
親愛的，沒問題，我會與你喝一轉
You got it, darling. I will draw circle.

254
00:22:15,060 --> 00:22:17,022
法拉斯，法拉斯，搞什麼
Faris, Faris? Put it.

255
00:22:21,029 --> 00:22:24,044
什麼……你們各位剛剛看到了嗎？
What the.. Did you guys just see that?

256
00:22:25,027 --> 00:22:27,039
他剛說什麼？
What did he just say?

257
00:22:31,075 --> 00:22:33,046
田納西，你聽到我說話嗎？
Tennessee, do you read me?

258
00:22:36,037 --> 00:22:38,039
田納西，聽得到嗎？
Tennessee, can you read me?

259
00:22:39,005 --> 00:22:40,093
田納西，你還好嗎？
Tennessee. You alright?

260
00:22:41,013 --> 00:22:43,010
那是他媽的什麼玩意？
What in the fuck was that?

261
00:22:43,030 --> 00:22:46,049
不知道，我得進來了
I don't know. Coming in. I'm coming in.

262
00:22:59,012 --> 00:23:01,095
大概是嚴重的傳輸損耗了吧
A rogue transmission loss, probably.

263
00:23:03,021 --> 00:23:06,028
你的頭盔能收到是因你飄遠了
Your helmet must have picked it up because you were so far out.

264
00:23:06,048 --> 00:23:08,083
已經超出了我們的通訊緩衝範圍
Past our communication buffers.

265
00:23:11,003 --> 00:23:12,048
媽媽，內里有音頻信息嗎？
Is there audio, Mother?

266
00:23:12,048 --> 00:23:15,093
正在整理，請稍等
Collating. A moment.

267
00:23:17,032 --> 00:23:20,060
奧姆艦長，我重新調整了傳輸設備
I reoriented the transmission, Captain Oram.

268
00:23:21,033 --> 00:23:23,084
應該只是回波，儀器損壞嚴重
Gotta be an echo, instruments took a lot of damage.

269
00:23:24,054 --> 00:23:27,094
自從我們來這裡，每46秒就會重覆接收一次
Been happening every 46 seconds ever since we got here

270
00:23:55,033 --> 00:23:56,092
這是約翰·丹佛的歌
That's fucking John Denver.

271
00:23:57,013 --> 00:23:58,062
那首《鄉村小路  帶我回家》啊
That's "Take Me Home, Country Roads".

272
00:23:58,062 --> 00:23:59,088
你一定是開玩笑
You gotta be kiddin.

273
00:23:59,088 --> 00:24:02,024
不，我絕不會開約翰·丹佛的玩笑
No, I never kid about John Denver.

274
00:24:02,024 --> 00:24:05,011
這兒還有定位數據
There is geometric data too.

275
00:24:05,011 --> 00:24:08,077
媽媽，請幫我們追蹤一下訊號來源
Mother, please track the signal to its source.

276
00:24:09,023 --> 00:24:10,057
正在追蹤
Working.

277
00:24:14,025 --> 00:24:16,099
傳輸來源已確定
Source of transmission located.

278
00:24:18,042 --> 00:24:22,001
訊號源於87區
Signal originates in the sector 87.

279
00:24:22,061 --> 00:24:25,032
赤經47.6度
Right ascension 47.6

280
00:24:25,053 --> 00:24:30,027
在我們當前位置下方24.3度
and a declination of 24.3 from our current location.

281
00:24:35,048 --> 00:24:38,030
看起來像是跟我們星系很像的一個主序星
She appears to be a main sequence star lot like our own.

282
00:24:38,098 --> 00:24:41,000
但年代久遠，非常之久遠
But old, very old.

283
00:24:41,000 --> 00:24:43,000
五顆行星
Five planets.

284
00:24:43,014 --> 00:24:45,024
等等，你們看
Wait. Look at that.

285
00:24:47,020 --> 00:24:49,019
第四號行星
Planet number four.

286
00:24:49,096 --> 00:24:53,001
第四號行星位處宜居帶
The planet number four is square in a habitable zone.

287
00:24:53,056 --> 00:24:55,056
事實上，在候補名單中它最合適
Prime candidate, in fact.

288
00:24:55,056 --> 00:25:00,040
地表重力有0.96G，有海洋和大陸
0.96 G's at surface, oceans, land mass.

289
00:25:00,040 --> 00:25:02,076
極有可能存有活躍的生態圈
High likely hood of a living biosphere.

290
00:25:03,043 --> 00:25:06,054
這比起源者6號所推測的更有希望啊
That's beyond the most optimistic projections of Oriage-6.

291
00:25:06,054 --> 00:25:09,082
我們已經掃描過整個區域了，為何仍會漏掉這個星球呢？
How did we miss this? We scanned the entire sector.

292
00:25:09,082 --> 00:25:11,099
里克斯，我們離那兒有多遠
Ricks, how far is it?

293
00:25:11,099 --> 00:25:13,040
很近
She's close.

294
00:25:13,096 --> 00:25:16,022
小飛躍的話，幾個星期就能到
Little jump. A few weeks.

295
00:25:16,022 --> 00:25:18,079
我們都不需要再回去進入休眠狀態
Wouldn't even have to go back into hyper sleep.

296
00:25:23,025 --> 00:25:27,007
那我們去起源者6號需要多久
And how long is it gonna take to get to Origae-6?

297
00:25:27,007 --> 00:25:29,006
七年，四個月
Seven years, four months.

298
00:25:29,006 --> 00:25:32,011
這是個該死的睡眠周期
That's one hell of a sleep cycle.

299
00:25:32,096 --> 00:25:36,070
長官，我負責地說，我們所有人
Sir, I think it's safe to say that none of us are too keen

300
00:25:36,070 --> 00:25:39,002
都不想再回到那些休眠艙里了
on getting back to one of those pods.

301
00:25:41,043 --> 00:25:45,057
也許我們該...走近點看看
Maybe we need to, um... Take a closer look.

302
00:25:47,073 --> 00:25:49,096
有人反對嗎？
Any objections?

303
00:25:53,028 --> 00:25:54,063
好的，里克斯，我們就
Okay, Ricks, let's..

304
00:25:55,015 --> 00:25:57,071
試一試靠近看清楚吧
Let's try to course and take a closer look.

305
00:25:58,030 --> 00:25:59,051
是，長官
Yes sir.

306
00:25:59,091 --> 00:26:02,027
艦長，我有些話想跟你說
Captain, can I talk to you for a second?

307
00:26:07,053 --> 00:26:08,096
你確定要這樣做嗎
Are you sure about this?

308
00:26:09,053 --> 00:26:10,084
你想說什麼？
How do you mean?

309
00:26:11,065 --> 00:26:14,095
我們找起源者6號就花了十年
We've spent a decade searching for Origae-6.

310
00:26:14,095 --> 00:26:18,027
我們審查過它，做過模擬，繪過地形圖
We vetted it, we ran the simulations, we mapped the terrain.

311
00:26:18,037 --> 00:26:20,005
- 這隻是我們的訓練內容     - 我明白
- It's what we trained for.     - I understand.

312
00:26:20,005 --> 00:26:21,062
現在我們就這樣拋掉之前的一切
And now we're gonna scrap all that

313
00:26:21,062 --> 00:26:23,075
為了追尋一個謎樣的訊號？
to chase a rogue transmission?

314
00:26:24,095 --> 00:26:26,017
你好好想想
Think about it.

315
00:26:26,017 --> 00:26:28,059
不可能有人類存在的地方出現了人類
A human being out there where there can't be any humans.

316
00:26:29,009 --> 00:26:30,097
一個隱形的星球就突然展現眼前
A hidden planet that turns up out of nowhere

317
00:26:30,097 --> 00:26:35,015
還碰巧特別適合我們居住，這好得難以置信
And just happens to be perfect for us. It's too good to be true.

318
00:26:35,015 --> 00:26:37,041
好得難以置信？  你這話是什麼意思？
Too good to be true? What do you mean by that?

319
00:26:37,041 --> 00:26:38,097
我們不知道那個地方到底有什麼鬼東西
We don't know what the fuck's out there.

320
00:26:38,097 --> 00:26:41,010
丹尼，也許我們只是漏掉了這星球而已
Maybe we just missed the planet, Danny.

321
00:26:41,030 --> 00:26:44,022
這不值得我們去冒這麼大的風險
This is a monumental risk not worth taking.

322
00:26:44,022 --> 00:26:45,078
我並未作出任何決定
I'm not committing to anything.

323
00:26:45,078 --> 00:26:48,090
我只是儘力走好眼前的路而已
I'm simply trying to navigate the path as it unfolds before us.

324
00:26:48,090 --> 00:26:50,029
這個星球有潛質成為
And this has the potential

325
00:26:50,030 --> 00:26:52,099
理想適合居住的殖民地
to be a better habitat for a colony.

326
00:26:52,099 --> 00:26:54,074
它有潛存，但我們真的不知道
It has the potential. We don't know that.

327
00:26:54,074 --> 00:26:56,001
再說，全體成員里
By the way, this crew nobody.

328
00:26:56,021 --> 00:26:58,072
沒有一個人會再想回到休眠艙了
Nobody wants to get back in the pods.

329
00:26:59,033 --> 00:27:00,033
是吧
Right?

330
00:27:01,014 --> 00:27:03,063
傳輸過來的訊號是一個人類的聲音
And that was a human voice in that transmission,

331
00:27:03,063 --> 00:27:06,042
我們有責任調查清楚
And it's our responsibility to investigate

332
00:27:06,042 --> 00:27:10,063
我們的責任是保護宇宙飛船上的兩千名殖民者
It's our responsibility to protect the 2,000 colonists on this ship.

333
00:27:12,026 --> 00:27:13,026
唏
Hey.

334
00:27:15,066 --> 00:27:17,085
我不是憑空做這個決定
I'm not free climbing here.

335
00:27:18,005 --> 00:27:21,053
我需要線索，我會好好利用這線索
I need ropes, and I'm using ropes.

336
00:27:21,073 --> 00:27:27,022
根據所有已得的數據，這會是個好判斷
This is good judgment, based on all the data available.

337
00:27:27,042 --> 00:27:28,050
你明白嗎？
You understand?

338
00:27:28,070 --> 00:27:31,098
作為你的二把手，我要提出正式抗議
As your second I need to protest. Officially.

339
00:27:33,045 --> 00:27:34,065
正式抗議？
Officially?

340
00:27:38,076 --> 00:27:41,032
好的，丹尼。 我會將它記錄在航行日誌里
Okay, Danny. I'll put it in the log.

341
00:27:43,002 --> 00:27:44,085
你可以走了
You're dismissed.

342
00:28:11,038 --> 00:28:12,073
我搜遍了所有頻道
I'm cycling through every channel

343
00:28:12,073 --> 00:28:14,093
只收到很多干擾和白噪音
but we're getting a lot of interference and white noise.

344
00:28:15,012 --> 00:28:16,042
還有些高頻回聲
Some high frequency echos.

345
00:28:16,042 --> 00:28:17,072
你聽到了什麼嗎？
Do you hear anything?

346
00:28:17,072 --> 00:28:20,067
只有幽靈朋友們的連續訊號
Just the continuing signal from our friendly ghost.

347
00:28:20,067 --> 00:28:23,002
帶我們進入它的軌道
Let's bring us in the closer orbit.

348
00:28:24,003 --> 00:28:26,005
登陸船準備
And prepare the lander.

349
00:28:26,057 --> 00:28:30,085
船體轉動中，啟動周邊位置護堰
Rolling progress, commencing circular location berm.

350
00:28:44,062 --> 00:28:46,044
毒氣水平在可容忍範圍內
Tox levels, withing tolerances.

351
00:28:46,055 --> 00:28:49,001
這個電離層好強
It's one hell of a strong ionosphere.

352
00:28:49,011 --> 00:28:50,030
是的，看得出來
Yeah, I see it.

353
00:28:50,040 --> 00:28:52,064
你之前用過登陸船嗎？
Hey, you ever done lander drop before?

354
00:28:52,085 --> 00:28:54,005
去你的
Fuck you.

355
00:28:54,015 --> 00:28:56,060
法拉斯，熱電離層好像有場等離子風暴
Faris, looks like a plasma storm in the thermosphere.

356
00:28:56,062 --> 00:28:58,063
估計時速有250公里
We got something like 250 kph.

357
00:28:58,073 --> 00:29:00,080
穿過去的話肯定夠受了
That's gonna be a motherfucker to fly through.

358
00:29:00,090 --> 00:29:02,074
