Crusoe on his island.

727
00:57:53,078 --> 00:57:56,023
我們的船員也感染了這種病毒嗎？
Our crew was infected with this virus?

728
00:57:56,080 --> 00:58:01,039
病原體是設計來感染任何非植物的生命體
The pathogen was designed to infect all non-botanical life forms.

729
00:58:01,050 --> 00:58:02,058
所有的動物
All the animals

730
00:58:03,028 --> 00:58:04,076
血肉之軀，就像你
The meat, if you will.

731
00:58:05,092 --> 00:58:07,080
不是直接殺死宿主，就是利用他們
Either kill them out right or use them

732
00:58:07,080 --> 00:58:10,097
作為孵化器孕育出一個混種生物
as incubators to spawn a hybrid form.

733
00:58:11,007 --> 00:58:12,084
極具攻擊性
Highly aggressive.

734
00:58:13,027 --> 00:58:14,077
我們被感染了嗎？
Have we been infected?

735
00:58:15,065 --> 00:58:17,086
如有你現在能感覺到了
You'd know by now.

736
00:58:17,096 --> 00:58:19,058
我們必須要確認
We have to be certain.

737
00:58:20,097 --> 00:58:23,015
我們不能把病原體帶回飛船上
We can't take this back to the ship.

738
00:58:23,035 --> 00:58:25,045
我們在執行一個殖民任務
We are a colony mission.

739
00:58:26,007 --> 00:58:27,088
是嗎？
Really?

740
00:58:27,098 --> 00:58:29,084
可非凡了
How extraordinary.

741
00:58:31,073 --> 00:58:33,026
有多少殖民者？
How many colonists?

742
00:58:35,057 --> 00:58:37,028
兩千多人
Over two thousand.

743
00:58:37,042 --> 00:58:39,018
好、好、好
Well, well, well.

744
00:58:39,081 --> 00:58:41,051
這麼多善良的靈魂
So many good souls.

745
00:58:42,001 --> 00:58:43,022
奧姆艦長
Captain Oram.

746
00:58:43,072 --> 00:58:47,087
地面傳送器沒法穿過這麼厚的石牆
Field transmitters are not gonna have a chance through all these stones.

747
00:58:49,019 --> 00:58:51,054
有沒有安全的通道直達樓頂？
Is there a safe way to get to the roof?

748
00:58:51,084 --> 00:58:53,014
當然有
Assure of it.

749
00:58:53,080 --> 00:58:56,022
請大家當作良家自便
And please do make yourself at home

750
00:58:56,042 --> 00:59:00,019
在這墓地做什麼也行
as much as you are able in this dire necropolis.

751
00:59:01,073 --> 00:59:02,082
歡迎弟兄
Welcome brother.

752
00:59:05,049 --> 00:59:06,065
這邊請
This way.

753
00:59:09,013 --> 00:59:12,026
大家伙兒，就讓我們在這兒待命吧
Everyone, let's uh.. Set up a stake here

754
00:59:17,039 --> 00:59:19,055
這裡有太多說不通的事情
There is so much here that doesn't make sense.

755
00:59:20,028 --> 00:59:21,077
我會跟他談談
I will talk to him.

756
00:59:23,056 --> 00:59:25,037
兄弟之間
Brother to brother.

757
00:59:30,081 --> 00:59:34,031
田納西？ 里克斯？ 請回答，你們聽到了嗎？
Tennessee? Ricks?  Come in! Do you copy?

758
00:59:35,053 --> 00:59:38,036
契約號，請回答。 這裡是遠征考察隊彙報
Covenant come in. This is expedition party reporting.

759
00:59:38,036 --> 00:59:39,062
你們聽到了嗎？
Do you read me?

760
00:59:40,079 --> 00:59:42,014
田納西？
Tennessee?

761
00:59:42,034 --> 00:59:44,034
田納西，里克斯，請回答
Tennessee, Ricks, come in.

762
00:59:44,074 --> 00:59:47,088
我不確定他們能在這暴風雨中能聽到你
I am not sure they'll hear you, through the storm.

763
00:59:48,081 --> 00:59:53,065
這裡的風暴非常猛烈，可覆蓋整個星球
They can be quite severe shielding the whole planet.

