Months.

768
01:00:05,000 --> 01:00:06,043
但定要堅持聯絡
But do keep at it.

769
01:00:07,076 --> 01:00:09,005
祝你們好運
Best of luck.

770
01:00:11,018 --> 01:00:14,072
契約號，請回答，這裡是遠征考察隊彙報，請回答
Covenant, come in, this is expedition party reporting. Come in.

771
01:00:15,081 --> 01:00:17,067
契約號，請回答
Covenant come in.

772
01:00:18,019 --> 01:00:21,052
