Mother, bring us to 80 km above the storm.

776
01:00:33,070 --> 01:00:35,018
稍等，請再等等
Hold on, just wait a minute.

777
01:00:35,028 --> 01:00:36,053
我們離星球越近
The closer we get to the planet.

778
01:00:36,053 --> 01:00:38,084
