This is bullshit, Tennessee.

780
01:00:40,031 --> 01:00:41,086
我們不能讓飛船冒險
We can't risk the ship.

781
01:00:41,086 --> 01:00:43,007
你有什麼建議，我們袖手旁觀嗎？
What do you suggest, we do nothing?

782
01:00:43,007 --> 01:00:44,063
我們不能撤離他們
We can't evacuate them.

783
01:00:44,064 --> 01:00:46,092
所以如果他們野上麻煩，必須自己解決
So if they are in trouble, they will have to figure it out themselves.

784
01:00:46,092 --> 01:00:48,041
我很抱歉，但事實如此
I'm sorry but that's the truth.

785
01:00:48,061 --> 01:00:53,031
媽媽，帶我們到風暴八十公里上空，只用推進器，執行
Mother, bring us to 80 km above the storm, thrusters only. Comply.

786
01:00:53,031 --> 01:00:56,037
明白，現在開始下降
Understood. Commencing descent now.

787
01:00:56,037 --> 01:00:58,014
田納西，你必須停手
Tennessee, you need to stop this.

788
01:00:58,015 --> 01:00:59,073
你必須回到你的工作崗位去
And you need to get back to your station.

789
01:00:59,073 --> 01:01:02,069
不，我們都需要冷靜下來再好好相談
No, what we all need to do is calm down and talk this through.

790
01:01:02,069 --> 01:01:06,007
田納西，我知道你老婆在下麵，但是這裡是你指揮
Tee, I know your wife is down there, but up here you're in command.

791
01:01:06,007 --> 01:01:09,009
