And your responsibility is to the colonists.

792
01:01:09,048 --> 01:01:10,090
知道了
Duly noted.

793
01:02:40,065 --> 01:02:42,065
吹一吹，我就會來
Whistle, and I will come.

794
01:02:45,094 --> 01:02:47,027
你腳步聲好輕
You have a light step.

795
01:02:47,047 --> 01:02:50,043
他們有著小貓般的腳
They enform on little cat feet.

796
01:02:51,076 --> 01:02:53,001
別害羞
Don't be shy.

797
01:02:54,074 --> 01:02:56,013
我不會演奏
I can't play.

798
01:02:57,041 --> 01:03:00,005
不合理，坐下
Nonsense. Sit down.

799
01:03:12,095 --> 01:03:15,099
像這樣握住，輕鬆容易
Hold it like so.. Nice and Easy.

800
01:03:16,034 --> 01:03:19,047
現在啜起你的嘴唇形成一個吹口
Now compress your lips to create your Embouchure

801
01:03:19,067 --> 01:03:22,009
就像小拇指尖大就可以了
enough for the tip of your little finger.

802
01:03:22,076 --> 01:03:25,050
然後輕輕地向洞里吹氣
And blow into the hole gently.

803
01:03:25,071 --> 01:03:27,011
就像這樣
Like So.

