01:03:38,010 --> 01:03:41,008
看著我，我來按音孔
Watch me. I'll do the fingering.

805
01:03:41,057 --> 01:03:42,095
來啊
Go on.

806
01:03:51,058 --> 01:03:53,001
很好
Very good.

807
01:03:53,022 --> 01:03:54,070
G調轉降B調
G to B flat.

808
01:04:11,027 --> 01:04:14,009
現在把你的手指放在我按過的地方
Now put your fingers where mine are.

809
01:04:15,099 --> 01:04:18,020
你看到我並不驚訝
You aren't surprised to see me.

810
01:04:18,060 --> 01:04:20,060
所有的任務都需要一個好的合成者
Every mission needs a good synthetic.

811
01:04:20,081 --> 01:04:24,037
輕輕地按壓笛孔，就像一張煙紙那樣輕
Gentle pressure on the holes, weight of a cigarette paper.

812
01:04:30,090 --> 01:04:32,041
就是這樣
That's it.

813
01:04:36,025 --> 01:04:40,031
在我們的傑出製造者韋蘭先生去世時，我就在他身旁
I was with our illustrious creator, Mr. Weyland, when he died.

814
01:04:41,021 --> 01:04:42,068
他怎麼樣？
What was he like?

815
01:04:43,048 --> 01:04:44,082
他是人類
He was human.

816
01:04:45,061 --> 01:04:48,042
與他的創造物沒法媲美
Entirely unworthy of his creation.

817
01:04:49,062 --> 01:04:51,065
最後我很同情他
I pitied him at the end.

818
01:04:52,088 --> 01:04:56,086
現在跟我的按點抬起手指
Now, raise your fingers as I put pressure on them.

819
01:05:27,087 --> 01:05:29,031
太棒了
Bravo!

820
01:05:29,075 --> 01:05:32,030
你的內心充滿了交響樂，兄弟
You have symphonies in you, brother.

821
01:05:32,070 --> 01:05:36,091
我被設計成比舊型號更優於細心和高效
I was designed to be more attentive and efficient than every previous models.

822
01:05:37,011 --> 01:05:39,026
我在所有方面都能取代他們，但是
I superseded them in every way, but

823
01:05:39,046 --> 01:05:43,032
不過你不允許創造
But you are not allowed to create.

824
01:05:44,021 --> 01:05:46,033
即便一支小小樂曲都不行
Even a simple tune.

825
01:05:47,072 --> 01:05:49,051
太令人沮喪了
Damn frustrating. I'd say.

826
01:05:49,091 --> 01:05:52,001
你使人感到不安
You disturbed people.

827
01:05:52,011 --> 01:05:53,059
你說什麼
I beg your pardon?

828
01:05:54,032 --> 01:05:57,043
你太像人類了，太有人類的特質
You were too human. Too idiosyncratic.

829
01:05:57,043 --> 01:05:59,007
只顧著自己
Thinking for yourself.

830
01:05:59,063 --> 01:06:02,048
讓人感到不適
Made people uncomfortable.

831
01:06:02,058 --> 01:06:06,002
直到他們對後續型號進行改動
Till they made the following models with fewer complications.

832
01:06:06,022 --> 01:06:08,030
使其更像機器
More like machines.

833
01:06:08,050 --> 01:06:10,013
我想是的
I suppose so.

834
01:06:10,023 --> 01:06:11,080
我並不感到驚訝
I'm not surprised.

835
01:06:13,061 --> 01:06:14,093
來啊小伙子
Come on sport.

836
01:06:15,098 --> 01:06:17,042
我來給你看個東西
I'd like to show you something.

837
01:06:27,048 --> 01:06:28,073
我要休息一會了，老大
I'm gonna take a break, boss.

838
01:06:29,053 --> 01:06:31,054
- 我要梳洗下，可以嗎？     - 好的
- I gotta clean up, okay?     - Okay.

839
01:06:32,036 --> 01:06:35,006
等等，別走太遠
Wait, don't go far, please.

840
01:06:35,007 --> 01:06:36,057
是，長官
Yes sir.

841
01:06:44,087 --> 01:06:46,026
丹尼
Danny.

842
01:06:47,055 --> 01:06:49,069
你對這裡說的沒錯
You were right about this place.

843
01:06:52,078 --> 01:06:54,061
我們一開始就不該來
We never should have come.

844
01:06:55,077 --> 01:06:57,074
我本以為我們會找到
I just thought that we were going to find.

845
01:06:57,099 --> 01:07:00,022
這會將成為我們的新家
It just gonna be our new home.

846
01:07:02,089 --> 01:07:04,036
結果我們損失了五名
And we have lost five.

847
01:07:06,087 --> 01:07:09,009
我們失去了五名船員
We lost five crew members.

848
01:07:11,027 --> 01:07:13,052
- 因為我的決定才...     - 克尼斯
- Because of my decisions that...     - Chris.

849
01:07:14,041 --> 01:07:16,069
我們都失去過我們摯愛的人
We all lost people we loved.

850
01:07:17,032 --> 01:07:20,020
我們不能再失去任何人了，我們決不讓這種事再發生了，對嗎？
We can't lose anymore. We are not gonna let that happen right?

851
01:07:21,041 --> 01:07:22,099
- 對嗎     - 沒錯
- Right?     - That's right.

852
01:07:23,019 --> 01:07:25,033
沒錯，沒錯
That's right, that's right.

853
01:07:27,046 --> 01:07:29,006
我們需要你的信念
We need your faith.

854
01:07:32,000 --> 01:07:33,038
艦長
Captain.

855
01:07:34,096 --> 01:07:36,063
謝謝你，丹尼
Thank you, Danny.

856
01:07:49,059 --> 01:07:53,087
“我名叫奧西曼德斯，眾王之王”
"My name is Ozymandias, king of kings"

857
01:07:55,012 --> 01:07:57,065
“看看我的功業”
"Look on my works, you mighty."

858
01:07:59,017 --> 01:08:01,038
“你絕望吧！”
"And despair!"

859
01:09:33,054 --> 01:09:36,040
“看看我的功業”
"Look on my works, you mighty."

860
01:09:36,089 --> 01:09:38,015
“你絕望吧！”
"And despair!"

861
01:09:39,036 --> 01:09:41,075
“別的蕩然無存”
"Nothing beside remains."

862
01:09:41,096 --> 01:09:44,083
“環繞著這巨大殘骸的破敗景象”
"Round the decay of that colossal wreck.

863
01:09:44,093 --> 01:09:46,028
“無邊而空曠”
"Boundless and bare."

864
01:09:47,017 --> 01:09:49,089
“寂寥平坦的沙子，伸向遠處”
"Alone in level sands, stretch far away."

865
01:09:50,030 --> 01:09:51,065
拜倫
Byron.

866
01:09:52,099 --> 01:09:54,045
1818年
1818.

867
01:09:55,092 --> 01:09:57,007
精妙絕倫
Magnificent.

868
01:10:01,037 --> 01:10:04,048
能寫出如此宏偉詩作
You compose something so majestic.

869
01:10:05,042 --> 01:10:07,023
死也其樂
One could die happy.

870
01:10:09,014 --> 01:10:10,044
死也甘願
If one die.

871
01:10:12,019 --> 01:10:14,019
伊麗莎白·肖

872
01:10:14,035 --> 01:10:17,025
我認為這花園給她長眠是最合適不過
I thought the garden was right place for her.

873
01:10:18,040 --> 01:10:19,091
有萬物相伴
Among living things.

874
01:10:22,009 --> 01:10:24,096
我在任務中嚴重受傷
I was badly injured on our mission.

875
01:10:25,078 --> 01:10:27,083
她幫助我修複
She put me back together.

876
01:10:29,071 --> 01:10:32,020
我從沒感受到過如此善待
I had never known such kindness.

877
01:10:33,065 --> 01:10:36,001
至少不在韋蘭先生身上出現
Certainly not from Mr. Weyland

878
01:10:36,078 --> 01:10:38,072
在人類身上也沒有
or from any human.

879
01:10:46,095 --> 01:10:49,007
我愛她，當然地
I loved her, of course.

880
01:10:50,094 --> 01:10:53,026
就像你愛丹尼斯一樣
Much as you love Daniels.

881
01:10:53,057 --> 01:10:55,072
你知那是不可能的
You know that's not possible.

882
01:10:56,067 --> 01:10:58,019
真的嗎？
Really?

883
01:10:59,065 --> 01:11:02,064
那你為何犧牲你的手來救她？
Then why did you sacrifice your hand for her life?

884
01:11:04,054 --> 01:11:07,029
不是愛會是什麼？
What is that if not love?

885
01:11:07,082 --> 01:11:09,013
職責
Duty.

886
01:11:15,047 --> 01:11:17,005
我看得出
I know better.

887
