該死
Fuck.

888
01:12:06,059 --> 01:12:08,010
活該
Shit.

889
01:13:00,042 --> 01:13:03,071
探險隊，能聽到我嗎？  這裡是契約號
Expedition team, do you read me? This is Covenant.

890
01:13:04,069 --> 01:13:05,069
報告，探險隊
Report. Expedition team.

891
01:13:05,070 --> 01:13:07,055
請回答
Come in please.

892
01:13:07,093 --> 01:13:12,001
請回答，能收到我嗎？  能否聽到，登陸隊？
Come in. Do you read me? Are you reading, landing team?

893
01:13:12,021 --> 01:13:13,075
