Yes, we read you. Can you hear me?

894
01:13:13,079 --> 01:13:14,071
能聽到，我們聽到你了
We hear you. We hear you.

895
01:13:14,075 --> 01:13:16,077
契約號，我們需要援助
Covenant, we need help.

896
01:13:16,078 --> 01:13:19,098
我們有人員傷亡，需要立即撤離
We've had casualties. We need immediate evacuation.

897
01:13:19,098 --> 01:13:22,014
重覆，立即撤離
I repeat, immediate evacuation.

898
01:13:22,015 --> 01:13:23,015
傷亡？
Casualties?

899
